    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Secondary prints pulled from a previously inked and pulled plate, produced intentionally for their lighter tonal quality, especially in monotype, collagraphy, or intaglio, they may also be called ghost prints.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
